<v-menu
  v-model="value"
  :transition="transition"
  offset-y
  v-bind="$attrs"
>
  <template v-slot:activator="{ attrs, on }">
    <v-btn
      :color="color"
      default
      min-width="200"
      rounded
      v-bind="attrs"
      v-on="on"
    >
      <slot />

      <v-icon>
        mdi-{{ value ? 'menu-up' : 'menu-down' }}
      </v-icon>
    </v-btn>
  </template>

  <v-sheet>
    <v-list dense>
      <v-list-item
        v-for="(item, i) in items"
        :key="i"
        @click="$(`click:action-${item.id}`)"
      >
        <v-list-item-content>
          <v-list-item-title v-text="item.text" />
        </v-list-item-content>
      </v-list-item>
    </v-list>
  </v-sheet>
</v-menu>
